// Wedding Map Strings

"MapString.jh.pottedplant": "Ever since Jumana shared that music can help flowers grow, Jonghyuk likes to sing to them from time to time. Whenever he thinks no one is watching, of course.",
"MapString.jh.console2": "A colorful gaming system loaded up with JunimoKart. Jonghyuk was humbled by your recent winning streak.",
"MapString.jh.punch2": "A heavy punching bag set up by Jonghyuk. It hardly budges after a friendly jab.",

//Jonghyuk's worn-out, delicate journal. You flip to a random page.#

"MapString.jh.journal1": "Jonghyuk's worn-out, delicate journal. You flip to a random page.#On Fall 3, {{PlayerName}} asked me what the date was. I told ${him^her}$ it was Fall 3. I love ${him^her}$ so much.",

//GNMT compat
"MapString.jh.journal1.GN": "Jonghyuk's worn-out, delicate journal. You flip to a random page.#On Fall 3, {{PlayerName}} asked me what the date was. I told {{PlayerName}} it was Fall 3. I love {{PlayerName}} so much.",

"MapString.jh.journal2": "Jonghyuk's worn-out, delicate journal. You flip to a random page.#The farmer stood outside my bedroom door with a gift over ${his^her}$ head. It was awfully sweet of ${him^her}$ to wait outside like that. ^^I don't know {{PlayerName}} that well, but maybe I should invite ${him^her}$ to our Sunberry Saturdays later? ^^I hope ${he^she}$ likes my cooking...^",

//GNMT compat
"MapString.jh.journal2.GN": "Jonghyuk's worn-out, delicate journal. You flip to a random page.#The farmer stood outside my bedroom door with a gift over their head. It was awfully sweet of {{PlayerName}} to wait outside like that. ^^I don't know the farmer that well, but maybe I should send an invite to our Sunberry Saturdays later? ^^I hope {{PlayerName}} likes my cooking...^",

"MapString.jh.journal3": "Jonghyuk's worn-out, delicate journal. You flip to a random page.#{{jhTrueName}} was really upset when his latest invention failed. I told him that failure doesn't happen because you don't succeed.^^He didn't fail. He just didn't succeed. Failure only happens once you give up. So really, he hasn't failed at all. That boy never gives up, not even a little... ^#That reminds me.^^We should really invest in more fire extinguishers. How on earth did he set the bathtub on fire? ^^That's weird and paranormal.^", //Do not delete or overwrite {{jhTrueName}}
"MapString.jh.journal4": "Jonghyuk's worn-out, delicate journal. You flip to a random page.#^\"Hyuk, do you still feel me hugging you? From now on, I will always be hugging you.\"^#When I was younger, Dad used to hug me so hard, it would hurt. ^^I would see him an hour later and he'd ask if I can still feel him hugging. If I said no, he'd hug me even harder. ^^I didn't really understand what he was trying to teach me until I was older...^#He was dying. ^^I convinced myself that if I just kept talking. He wouldn't die. So I talked and talked and talked. ^^My family said I couldn't keep doing this forever. When I was about to leave his side, Dad opened his eyes and squeezed my hand one last time...^# ^\"Do you still feel me hugging you? From now on, I will always be hugging you.\"^# ^\"Take care of them, Hyuk.\"^",
"MapString.jh.journal5": "Jonghyuk's worn-out, delicate journal. You flip to a random page.#Man... caring about other people is hard work. It was easier when I didn't have to. ^^But I ended up giving that boy a piece of my mind.^#^I told him that if you make a promise, you keep it. ^If you make a mistake, you apologize. ^And if you give someone a dream, you defend it to the end.^#^Then I gave him a spare key to my apartment. If he's going to keep breaking into my home, he might as well live here. ^^It was getting kind of lonely anyways.^#^What a troublesome kid. Now if I could just get him to stop crying and calling me 'Boss'...^",
"MapString.jh.journal6": "Jonghyuk's worn-out, delicate journal. You flip to a random page.#Dear, {{PlayerName}}.^The love of my life.^My wild heart. ^^I doubt you'll ever read this, so I am writing to you with all the love in my heart. ^^Just as my heart yearns for you, so does my body. I have purchased several items you will like. Upon your return from work, we shall proceed to shatter our bed frame and--^#You close the journal. That's enough reading for today.",

"MapString.jh.journal7": "Jonghyuk's worn-out, delicate journal. You flip to a random page.#You know, it's wild. ^^{{PlayerName}} has no idea how lovable ${he^she}$ is. Like genuinely. People feel lucky just to know ${him^her}$. {{PlayerName}} can walk into a room and the energy shifts even if ${he^she}$ can't notice it.^^Whenever I hear ${him^her}$ laugh, it sounds just like home.^",

//GNMT compat
"MapString.jh.journal7.GN": "Jonghyuk's worn-out, delicate journal. You flip to a random page.#You know, it's wild. ^^{{PlayerName}} has no idea how amazing it is to be here in my life. Like genuinely. People feel lucky just to know {{PlayerName}}. {{PlayerName}} can walk into a room and the energy shifts even if no one notices.^^Whenever I hear {{PlayerName}} laugh, it sounds just like home.^",

//Previously missed Lani x Jonghyuk event:
"LanhyukBoxing.0": "Hey, Jonghyuk~$9",
"LanhyukBoxing.1": "...$28",
"LanhyukBoxing.2": "I'm coming in!$11",
"LanhyukBoxing.3": "Wha--?$29",
"LanhyukBoxing.4": "Rise and shine!",
"LanhyukBoxing.5": "... Lani?",
"LanhyukBoxing.6": "Hey. I'm here to rant about stuff.$u#$b#...Unless this is a bad time?$7",
"LanhyukBoxing.7": "Nah. I'll always have time for you.$h",
"LanhyukBoxing.8": "Okay, great!",
"LanhyukBoxing.9": "So I read your self-help book on managing anger and it's been wildly unhelpful.$s",
"LanhyukBoxing.10": "Lani opens the book to a worn-out page marked by colorful sticky-notes.",
"LanhyukBoxing.11": "'Think before you speak. 'Forgiveness is a noble goal.'$6#$b#Hilarious they think I can filter, but like, how are people supposed to know they fucked up if I can't even SAY when they fucked up?$5#$b#Of course if I, a woman, say anything--then I'm automatically a bitch, right?$5",
"LanhyukBoxing.12": "YOBA it's infuriating.",
"LanhyukBoxing.13": "Let me guess... Rough day at work?$11#$b#Also, easy on the book, Lani. Elias lent that to me.",
"LanhyukBoxing.14": "Sorry. Work is just... Ugh.$s#$b#My coworkers don't know how to do literally anything sometimes, and then one of them had the nerve to tell me how to do my job.#$b#Obviously wasn't gonna fly with me because they were completely wrong. So I corrected them.$u#$b#Then I got reported for being too mean, so now I'm 'working on my behavior.'$11",
"LanhyukBoxing.15": "That sounds so corporate, I'd want to throw myself out the window.$5",
"LanhyukBoxing.16": "Y'know, I might have just the thing to make you feel better. Release all that tension of yours.$11#$b#...And it's a great outlet for my emotions whenever I'm feeling pent up and bothered.$15",
"LanhyukBoxing.17": "...What are we talkin' about?$9",
"LanhyukBoxing.18": "You can use my sandbag! Talk it out with your fists.$u",
"LanhyukBoxing.19": "Oh.$8#$b#Not how I was thinking this was gonna go, but yeah, sure!$1",
"LanhyukBoxing.20": "First we need to make sure your hands are wrapped up properly or you could seriously hurt yourself.$10#$b#I used to wear socks with a shirt inside them as gloves when I first started out.$11",
"LanhyukBoxing.21": "Wouldn't that hurt?$7",
"LanhyukBoxing.22": "Wasn't too bad, but we all have to start somewhere. Here, try these on.$13",
"LanhyukBoxing.23": "Okay, this is actually pretty liberating. I'm not sure I'm punching right, though.$7",
"LanhyukBoxing.24": "Remind me to never get on your bad side! But yeah, we just need to adjust your form.$h",
"LanhyukBoxing.25": "People think punching is all about the arms, but it involves the entire body.$8#$b#Starting from the ground and driving up through your core... Your hip and shoulder should swing with the momentum... as you punch through...$12",
"LanhyukBoxing.26": "Uh-huh...$9#$b#(He's too close...! Do I smell? Can he see my acne scars?? OH YOBA I HOPE I DON'T SMELL...)$9#$b#(HE'S TOO CLOSE!!!)$9",
"LanhyukBoxing.27": "Lani... are you listening?$8",
"LanhyukBoxing.28": "Uh-huh...$9",
"LanhyukBoxing.29": "You dork. Here, watch me.$11",
"LanhyukBoxing.30": "Make sure to always guard your cheek with your arm. Stance should be wider than your shoulders...$10",
"LanhyukBoxing.31": "...Wow.$l",
"LanhyukBoxing.32": "Whew!",
"LanhyukBoxing.33": "And now it's your turn!$h#$b#Though... I really like seeing you like this. Makes me feel like I can take on the whole world.$4#$b#That's a bit silly of me, huh?$9",
"LanhyukBoxing.34": "Wow. Okay, I, uh... whew. WHEW... is it hot in here? Am I dying?$l",
"LanhyukBoxing.35": "Oh no... are you feeling alright?$19",
"LanhyukBoxing.36": "Yeah!$1#$b#Well, no, but I think I just need a little fresh air so I don't die.$8#$b#We, um, should definitely do this again. No, seriously, you made my day and now I have A LOT to think about!$7#$b#Okay-see-you-later-bye!$8",


