//10 Heart

"jhMount.0": "Hi, honey.$u",
"jhMount.1": "Enjoying the mountain air?$h#$b#I went on a hike earlier to calm my nerves. Now I'm just admiring the sky.$8",
"jhMount.2": "You know... I asked {{jhTrueName}} the other day if he ever missed Zuzu. And you know what he said?$h#$b#His favorite part of moving to Sunberry was listening to the sounds of trees.$u#$b#He could never do that in the city.$8",
"jhMount.3": "I've never stopped to consider doing something as simple as that before.#$b#Imagine me--listening to trees. The swaying of branches in the wind and rustling of leaves.$h#$b#It's so peaceful. Yet at the same time, it's also so frustrating.#$b#I'm just now appreciating the beautiful things in my life.$14",
"jhMount.4": "Well anyway, it's easy to lose track of time up in the mountains.$8#$b#Would you like to join me? The ground's kind of soft.$8",
"jhMount.5": "You want me to lie on the ground?",
"jhMount.6": "I mean, we can cuddle if you want. I wouldn't say no to that.$9",
"jhMount.7": "I guess I can join you for a bit.",
"jhMount.8": "Yes. Absolutely yes.",
"jhMount.9": "You're such a dork. Move over.",
"jhMount.10": "Jonghyuk adjusts himself so you can lay more comfortably against his broad chest.",
"jhMount.11": "His arm naturally drapes around your side, cushioning you from the uneven surface of the ground.",
"jhMount.12": "There we go! Feeling comfortable?",
"jhMount.13": "Jonghyuk holds you with the utmost gentleness.",
"jhMount.14": "You're warm.",
"jhMount.15": "I could get used to this.",
"jhMount.16": "That's good. I'll have you know that I'm an expert cuddler.",
"jhMount.17": "And you fit perfectly in my arms.",
"jhMount.18": "I've no artist's soul, so I can't exactly say why the sight of a sunset is so beautiful.",
"jhMount.19": "But it never fails to stir my heart.",
"jhMount.20": "Sometimes you have to pause what you're doing and take in the moment. Whether that's listening to the trees or looking up at the sky.",
"jhMount.21": "Mundane moments like these are meant to be shared with good company.",
"jhMount.22": "And you know how much I love having a fantastic view right in front of me. The sky is pretty too, I guess.",
"jhMount.23": "You pause to think for a moment.",
"jhMount.24": "Wait, are you talking about me?", //First Option
"jhMount.25": "Me too. You're a close second though.", //Second Option

//First option
"jhMount_Answer1.0": "Of course.",
"jhMount_Answer1.1": "There's no one else. Nothing can ever compare to you.",
"jhMount_Answer1.2": "Even if you like to dig through trashcans, you're still number one in my heart.",

//Second Option Response
"jhMount_Answer2.0.false": "Damn. The sky is gorgeous, after all.",
"jhMount_Answer2.0.true": "Haha. The sky is gorgeous, after all.",
"jhMount_Answer2.1": "Imagine being second only to the setting sun in your eyes.",
"jhMount_Answer2.2": "I'm that good, huh?",

"jhMountLoop1.0": "Jonghyuk chuckles, the vibrations rumbling against your body.",
//Player choices
"jhMountLoop1.1": "Would you be quiet?", //charm
"jhMountLoop1.2": "Oh my god, shut up.", //shut
"jhMountLoop1.3": "That's not funny.", //charm

//shut response
"jhMount_Shut.0": "Hahaha! Make me.",
"jhMount_Shut.1": "*Jonghyuk chuckles, and you're drawn to the tremor of his lips. You pause and think to yourself.",

//charm response
"jhMount_Charm.0": "I'm sorry. Let me charm that frown off your pretty face.",
"jhMount_Charm.1": "Please don't be upset with me. Please, honey?",
"jhMount_Charm.2": "*As Jonghyuk begs with you, failing to hide his grin, you're drawn to the tremor of his lip.",

"jhMountLoop2.0": "*IF you want to swipe that smug arrogant grin off his face, now's your chance.",
"jhMountLoop2.1": "Jonghyuk is lost in the moment.",
"jhMountLoop2.2": "The audacity. Kiss his stupid face.",
"jhMountLoop2.3": "Let him win. For now.",

//Kiss
"jhMount_Kiss.0": "{{PlayerName}}. My wild heart.",
"jhMount_Kiss.1": "I have something to confess. Something that's been weighing on my mind.",
"jhMount_Kiss.2": "I've been dreaming about you.",
"jhMount_Kiss.3": "Like, a lot a lot.",
"jhMount_Kiss.4": "It's a recurring dream.",
"jhMount_Kiss.5": "And each time I wake, I just... I don't know. I feel just a bit more hollow inside.",
"jhMount_Kiss.6": "His expression goes blank.",
"jhMount_Kiss.7": "Okay. Wow.",
"jhMount_Kiss.8": "What's that supposed to mean?",

//No kiss (same as above with slight variations. Only difference is "Kiss.0" and "Calm.0", everything else is the same)
"jhMount_Calm.0": "{{PlayerName}}...",
"jhMount_Calm.1": "I have something to confess. Something that's been weighing on my mind.",
"jhMount_Calm.2": "I've been dreaming about you.",
"jhMount_Calm.3": "Like, a lot a lot.",
"jhMount_Calm.4": "It's a recurring dream.",
"jhMount_Calm.5": "And each time I wake, I just... I don't know. I feel just a bit more hollow inside.",
"jhMount_Calm.6": "His expression goes blank.",
"jhMount_Calm.7": "Okay. Wow.",
"jhMount_Calm.8": "What's that supposed to mean?",

"jhMount_explain1.0": "I love spending time with you, {{PlayerName}}. Sometimes I wish these moments would never end.",
"jhMount_explain1.1": "I dream about how nice it would be to grow old together with you.",
"jhMount_explain1.2": "But that's the thing.",
"jhMount_explain1.3": "You'll never grow old to me. I can't envision it.",
"jhMount_explain1.4": "Even if I add up all the joy in my life, nothing compares to you.",
"jhMount_explain1.5": "Then when I wake up all by myself, it feels like the sky is falling apart.",
"jhMount_explain1.6": "The world ended, but I'm still here.",
"jhMount_explain1.7": "All the walls I've built come tumbling down. And I'm left with nothing to hide from these feelings of mine.",
"jhMount_explain1.8": "I'm an absolute mess, but loving you is a good problem to have.",
"jhMount_explain1.9": "He looks at you expectantly.",
"jhMount_explain1.10": "Wait.",
"jhMount_explain1.11": "What did you say?",
"jhMount_explain1.12": "{{PlayerName}}, I am madly in love with you.",
"jhMount_explain1.13": "Yoba, I am SO into you.",
"jhMount_explain1.14": "I'll say it over a hundred million times. You make me the happiest man alive.",
"jhMount_explain1.15": "...Can I kiss you?",
"jhMount_explain1.16": "His ears are turning red.",
"jhMount_explain1.17": "Of course.",
"jhMount_explain1.18": "Not now.",

"jhMount_explain2.0": "*Without a word, you burrow deeper into his arms, your presence wrapping around him like a second skin.",
"jhMount_explain2.1": "*Your fingers find their way into his hair, threading through soft brown strands in the way that make his eyes flutter shut.",
"jhMount_explain2.2": "*And that was it. That effortless care. That quiet, unconditional love. It reminds him of why he had fallen in with you in the first place.",
"jhMount_explain2.3": "Thank you, @. You're everything I could ever ask for.$l#$b#I won't be subtle about loving you. Not now. Not ever.$25",
"jhMount_explain3.0": "Thank you, @. You're everything I could ever ask for.$l#$b#I won't be subtle about loving you. Not now. Not ever.$25", //Same as above 

// WEDDING

"WeddingJonghyuk.0": "@, my beloved.$l#$b#We're really doing it. We're finally getting married!$9",
"WeddingJonghyuk.1": "Just saying it fills my heart in ways words can barely hold.$l#$b#From this day forward, I'm not just yours in soul and promise... I'm yours in name, in life, in every little moment we share.$9",
"WeddingJonghyuk.2": "I wish this moment could last forever, but the ceremony is just up ahead.$8#$b#All our loved ones are waiting for us. We can't keep them waiting too long now, can we?$u",
"WeddingJonghyuk.3": "Jonghyuk offers you his hand. Your fingers gently entwine before interlocking fully.",
"WeddingJonghyuk.4": "Lightly running your thumb over the back of his hand, he relaxes into your touch.",
"WeddingJonghyuk.5": "I love you, @.$h",
"WeddingJonghyuk.6": "*sniffle*",
"WeddingJonghyuk.7": "Boss asked ME to be his best man. Can you believe it?$8#$b#This is the happiest day of my life.$8",
"WeddingJonghyuk.8": "Grandma said that today would be a new chapter of our lives.$u#$b#So let's do our very best today! Just like we rehearsed.$h",
"WeddingJonghyuk.9": "Yeah. *sniffle* I'm ready.$h",
"WeddingJonghyuk.10": "Friends, family, and loved ones. We gather here today to celebrate love, a lifelong bond.$h#$b#There's no better feeling than finding your person.$h#$b#The one who really sees you. The one who loves you endlessly.#$b#The one who wishes to spend the rest of their life by your side.$h",
"WeddingJonghyuk.11": "Bring forth the Mermaid Pendant.",
"WeddingJonghyuk.12": "Y-Yes!$4",
"WeddingJonghyuk.13": "This pendant represents a symbol of tides unbroken, just as your love shall be.#$b#May your devotion to each other be as deep as the ocean itself.#$b#It is my great honor to unite @ and Jonghyuk in the bonds of marriage on this beautiful day.$u",
"WeddingJonghyuk.14": "It is now time to exchange vows.",
"WeddingJonghyuk.15": "@, do you take Cho Jonghyuk to be your Life Partner?",
"WeddingJonghyuk.16": "I do.",
"WeddingJonghyuk.17": "Do you promise to love, honor, and cherish Jonghyuk, in sickness and in health?#$b#To share your harvest, your laughter, and your heart with him for as long as you both shall live?",
"WeddingJonghyuk.18": "I do.",
"WeddingJonghyuk.19": "Do you, Cho Jonghyuk, take @ to be your Life Partner?",
"WeddingJonghyuk.20": "I do.$l",
"WeddingJonghyuk.21": "Do you promise to love, honor, and cherish @, in sickness and in health?#$b#To stand by @ through every harvest, regardless of drought and storm?",
"WeddingJonghyuk.22": "I do.$h#$b#@. I stand here not just as your groom, but as the man who will spend every waking moment making sure you feel utterly, devastatingly happy.$9",
"WeddingJonghyuk.23": "@... Jonghyuk... #$b#I'm honored to be here and witness you seal the bond of your love.$h#$b#As the administrator of Sunberry Village, and regional bearer of the matrimonial seal, I now pronounce you as forever life partners!$u",
"WeddingJonghyuk.24": "You may kiss.$h",

//speech bubbles
"WeddingJonghyuk.25": "Yay!",
"WeddingJonghyuk.Sterling": "Way to go, Nacho!!",
"WeddingJonghyuk.26": "Congrats!",

"WeddingJonghyuk.27": "Before we met, I didn’t know what it meant to truly need someone.$8#$b#But now? I crave you like the sun. You complete me in ways I cannot explain in words.$h#$b#Today we didn’t just seal a vow. We began our forever. And I’ll spend the rest of mine loving you with everything I am.$9#$e#Married by day, unwrapped by night... I have a few ideas how we can spend our honeymoon, @.$16",

"Festivals.FashionShow.Jonghyuk": "I'm a little behind the times so I wanted to check out the latest fashion trends.$h#$b#I'd invite my sister, but she's studying abroad. She has a knack for this kind of stuff.#$b#We used to go thrift shopping, and she'd pick out so many hidden gems within minutes. She could honestly make anything work.$h",

// marriage update

  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.patio_Jonghyuk.1": "Huh? You wanna know how I stay so fit?$11#$e#Well, it's no secret that you're my greatest motivation.$16#$b#After all, this body belongs to you, babe.$9#$b#%He steps into your space and flexes his chest, playfully bouncing his pecs.#$e#It's a good day to work out. Hope you're still raring to go, especially with all the crops and animals.$h",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.patio_Jonghyuk.2": "%Jonghyuk is wiping pearls of sweat from his brow with his shirt, the movement briefly exposing the defined ridges of his sculpted abs.#$b#Hello, my wild heart. There's nothing like a good pump to really get the blood flowing.$u#$e#No matter how heavy your day is, I’ll always be here to remind you that you belong right here, with me.$8#$b#Loving you is the easiest, most natural thing I’ve ever done.$h",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.patio_Jonghyuk.3": "My allergies to %pet are getting a whole lot better! Marnie suggested some hypoallergenic diets for our critters and they work like a charm.$8#$b#Now I can give $pet all the belly rubs and pets.$h#$e#What? You think %pet is cute? Well, I'm obviously cuter.$u",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spouseRoom_Jonghyuk.1": "I wanted to make the morning a little special for us so I whipped up a little something.$8#$b#But you know what? Nothing beats the comfort of just being with you at home.[210 211 395]$h#$b#Just make sure to kiss the chef on your way out, mmm?$l",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spouseRoom_Jonghyuk.2": "Hi, Love. The farm life isn't quite what I imaged.$13#$b#You've turned moments into memories I'll treasure forever.$11#$b#Just knowing I bring you happiness and boundless love... there's no greater gift I could ask for.$9",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spouseRoom_Jonghyuk.3": "We could watch the 'Queen of Sauce' together. But knowing you, I'd likely end up getting lost in the sauce.#$b#You can be kind of distracting. It's a good problem to have, I assure you. After all, you have my fully undivided attention.$l",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spouseRoom_Jonghyuk.4": "Aigoo... my @ senses are tingling. Something's off.#$b#What are you scheming this time, oh darling ${husband^wife}$ of mine?$11#$b#$y '*How should you respond?$h_> Would you still love me if I was a worm?_Bahah! Seriously? That's what was on your mind?$u*No star burns brighter than the love I feel for you! Even if you were a wriggly little worm.$h*%Jonghyuk plants a tender kiss on your forehead.*Mwah.$h^Mwah. A happy wife is a happy life.$15_> Boop him on the nose._Huh. This your plan, mm? Testing my patience while looking irresistibly cute?$u*You and I both know you want more than just to boop my nose, my love.$h*I'll make sure you never forget what happens if you keep teasing me like this.$15_> Kiss him on the cheek._You really know how to spoil me in the most beautiful ways, mmm?$u*Well, if you keep this up, I might just have to remind you how much I appreciate all that attention.$h*I'll make sure to return the favor in ways that'll leave you... panting.$15'", //Be careful not to erase or overwrite the "_", "*" and the ">"
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spouseRoom_Jonghyuk.5": "I was doing the laundry and you'll never believe what happened.$12#$b#I found my favorite sock! And I know where the other one is!$11#$b#My socks are finally going to be reunited and be so happy.$13#$b#...I swear I'm not this scatterbrained. I just sometimes confuse my load with yours and they end up all washed together.$19#$e#What, did you need something? Wanted to see see me in my special socks?$11#$b#$y '*How should you respond?$h_> Just your socks?_Ayo? Damn, you're making me blush.$h*I mean, if that's something you're into, then hell yeah. I'll give you a real show and put them on nice and slow.$15*_> You forgot your kiss._You really know how to spoil me in the most beautiful ways.$h*Well, c'mere. I won't be subtle about loving you. Not now. Not ever.$l'",

  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spouseRoom_Jonghyuk.6": "I don't mind if you read from my journal. I've had it for years now.#$b#I find journaling as a form of mediation. Helps me unravel my own feelings and figure out what I want to do at the moment.$h#$e#It's nice knowing you're interested in my drabbles. I enjoy sharing bits of my past with you like this.$8",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spouseRoom_Jonghyuk.7": "My allergies to %pet are getting a whole lot better! Marnie suggested some hypoallergenic diets for our critters and they work like a charm.$8#$b#Now I can give $pet all the belly rubs and pets.$h#$e#What? You think %pet is cute? Well, I'm obviously cuter.$u",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spouseRoom_Jonghyuk.8": "I've never been good at soft things. But you? You make me want to be gentle.$h#$b#How about we cuddle on the couch? I'll hold you with care, kiss with reverence, and speak to you with utmost tenderness.$16#$b#Aha, sorry if I'm getting a little sappy. I'll love you even more shamelessly.$9",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spouseRoom_Jonghyuk.9": "Aigoo... my @ senses are tingling. Something's off.#$b#What are you scheming this time, oh darling ${husband^wife}$ of mine?$11#$b#$y '*How should you respond?$h_> Would you still love me if I was a worm?_Bahah! Seriously? That's what was on your mind?$u*No star burns brighter than the love I feel for you! Even if you were a wriggly little worm.$h*%Jonghyuk plants a tender kiss on your forehead.*Mwah.$h^Mwah. A happy wife is a happy life.$15_> Boop him on the nose._Huh. This your plan, mm? Testing my patience while looking irresistibly cute?$u*You and I both know you want more than just to boop my nose, my love.$h*I'll make sure you never forget what happens if you keep teasing me like this.$15_> Kiss him on the cheek._You really know how to spoil me in the most beautiful ways, mmm?$u*Well, if you keep this up, I might just have to remind you how much I appreciate all that attention.$h*I'll make sure to return the favor in ways that'll leave you... panting.$15'", //Be careful not to erase or overwrite the "_", "*" and the ">"
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spouseRoom_Jonghyuk.10": "Hello, my dear ${hubby^wifey}$. Love of my life. The other half of my soul.$8#$b#$y '*How should you respond?$h_> Give him a kiss._If this isn't how I'm greeted every time, I'm gonna start the day all pouty and heartbroken, my beloved.$16*You've set the bar way too high now... Guess you'll just have to keep spoiling me like this forever, mmm?$9_> Give him a hug._If I could freeze time just to stay wrapped in your arms a little longer, I would. You make every sunrise worth waking up to.$9*Good morning, @. My wild heart.$h_> What's for breakfast?_Oh, you know! The usual. I'm starting to think that you fell in love with me just for my cooking![210 211 350]$u*Just make sure to kiss the chef on your way out, mmm?$l'", //Be careful not to erase or overwrite the "_", "*" and the ">"

