//Special Dates

  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.SpouseStardrop": "Good morning, honey. I want you to know that you deserve the world. This is just a fraction of what I owe you.$8#$b#I just want to see you smile. That's the only thing I need today.$h#$e#The truth is, I am madly in love with you.$16#$b#Every word I say comes from a place of wanting to protect your heart. You are everything to me.$9",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.FlowerDance_Accept_Spouse": "You're asking me to dance?$19#$b#I thought that was already a given. I was yours from the start.$h#$b#I vow to never take these moments for granted. To never forget how lucky I am that somehow, against every odd, you chose me, my darling ${husband^wife}$.$l",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.FlowerDance_Accept_Spouse.GN": "You're asking me to dance?$19#$b#I thought that was already a given. I was yours from the start.$h#$b#I vow to never take these moments for granted. To never forget how lucky I am that somehow, against every odd, you chose me, my darling {{Hana.GNMTokens/SpouseNoun}}.$l",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.funLeave_Jonghyuk": "No matter how far I roam, I'll always find my way back to you.$8#$b#Your arms are my home, and there's no place I'd rather return to.$u",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.funReturn_Jonghyuk": "I just want you to know how proud I am of everything you're doing.$8#$b#Even when things feel tough or uncertain, I see the strength in you to keep pushing forward.$h#$b#You have this incredible drive, and I truly believe you're destined to achieve all the amazing things you've set your heart on.$13#$b#And remember, every step you take is progress. I'll be right here cheering you on every single day.$17", 
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spring_Jonghyuk": "I just want you to know how proud I am of everything you're doing.$8#$b#Even when things feel tough or uncertain, I see the strength in you to keep pushing forward.$h#$b#You have this incredible drive, and I truly believe you're destined to achieve all the amazing things you've set your heart on.$13#$b#And remember, every step you take is progress. I'll be right here cheering you on every single day.$17",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spring_13": "Good luck at the Egg Festival tomorrow. If you win, I'll give you a special prize.$u#$e#What, you want to know what it is?$13#$e#Mmm, greedy little thing, aren’t you? But lucky for you, I’m feeling generous enough to give you a hint.$11#$b#It's sweet enough to make you melt, and sinful enough to keep you up all night.$15#$e#Want a sneak peek?$l", //EGG FESTIVAL
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spring_14": "You were amazing yesterday. You really know how to spoil me in the most beautiful ways.$13#$b#If you keep this up, I might just have to remind you how much I appreciate all that attention.$11#$e#Should I cook you something egg-related? Or maybe you're tired of all the eggs...$13",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spring_23": "Your hubby's feeling particularly needy and starved for affection today.$h#$b#But I'll be patient and sweep you off your feet tomorrow at the dance.$16#$b#The flowers are pretty, but not as beautiful as the life I have with you.$9", //FLOWER DANCE 
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spring_24": "Today's the day! Now go ${have some fun and let loose.^be the stunning goddess you are today.}$ $h#$b#But don't forget, I'll be thinking about you nonstop.$9", //FLOWER DANCE
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spring_25": "I'm falling for you all over again. Yesterday didn't just feel like a storybook, it was one!$h#$b#And you were the most breathtaking page, @.$15#$b#You looked like spring wrapped in sunshine. Every laugh, and every glance you gave me felt like a secret meant only for my heart.$8#$b#I could spend forever chasing that magic with you.$u", //FLOWER DANCE aftermath 
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spring_28": "It's Spanner's birthday today! Or at least, it's the day he came into my life.$1#$b#We don't actually know when he was born, so he decided that today is the day we would celebrate.$8#$b#I hate getting so worked up and emotional, but from then on I swore we'd make even happier memories together.$11#$e#Do you mind giving this to him? [220]$u#$e#You should have seen the first time he's ever had a bite of cake.$h",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.summer_11": "You wanna know what I put in the potluck?$8#$b#Babe, you know me. I like things hot and spicy, hehe.$u",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.summer_Jonghyuk": "Mmm, darling, that beach day is burning a permanent mark on my mind.$h#$b#Just you and me, tangled in the sand, the sea crashing around us while we write our names in the sand.$15#$b#$y '*How should you respond?_> Let's build a sand castle!_A castle just for my ${darling prince^captive queen}$? You should know that this dragon doesn't like to share its treasure.$h*If you ever try to leave, I'll leave you breathless before the sun even sets.$16_> No takebacks!_No cancellations allowed? Perfect.$h*Because I plan to love you all day long, float with the rhythm of the waves, and leave you breathless before the sun even sets.$9_> Sounds fun!_Perfect. I got a new swimsuit I wanted to show you.$16*I'll leave you breathless before the sun even sets.$9'", //Be careful not to erase or overwrite the "_", "*" and the ">"
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.summer_5": "Today feels different. Like the beginning of something eternal for you and me.$8#$b#I don't need the sun when I have your smile... and I don't need anything else as long as I get to hold your hand.$8#$b#Thank you for loving me the way you do, @. My beloved.$h", //birthday
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.summer_28": "Did you know that clinging to your hubby is the best remedy for heatstroke?$17#$b#$y '*How should you respond?_> You sure about that?_Well, maybe it's not the exact cure, but it definitely the sweetest side effect.$16*I get to keep my right in my arms... tight and secure. And only mine.$9_> Really?_Well, maybe it's not the exact cure, buuut it definitely the sweetest side effect.$16*I get to keep my right in my arms... tight and secure. And only mine.$9_> I doubt it._You caught me red-handed. I just wanted to excuse to hold you tight and close.$u'",  //Be careful not to erase or overwrite the "_", "*" and the ">"
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.fall_Jonghyuk": "Time is constantly changing. The season changes color as the nights become cooler.#$b#The only thing that won't change is the way I feel about you.$h",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.fall_15": "Hey there, love. I have a good feeling about tomorrow.$h#$b#Ripley might be a close contender, but I have no doubt you'll win the fair. Let me know if you any help with the heavy lifting.$8#$b#I know you're plenty strong, but you can put me to work.$h#$e#Should I flex a little in front of the judges? You know, to score us some more points.$u",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.fall_16": "Okay, darling. Hear me out.$8#$b#The spinning wheel was calling to me. And your hubby is a bonafide winner.$u#$b#I even have this premium certificate for bragging rights to prove it! It only cost me 50 Star Tokens.$h#$e#But seriously! The wheel was a legitimate 50% chance of winning and succeeding.$a#$b#Ain't no way the wheel landed ten consecutive times on orange.$18",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.fall_25": "Oh no. There's going to be a full moon tonight and I forgot to take my heat suppressant pills!$16#$b#Whatever will I do? All alone and vulnerable in front of my strong and reliable ${husband^wife}$?$9#$b#$y '*How should you respond?_> Jonghyuk, what the heck?_Bahaha! Woof! Arf arf! Ruff. Growl.$11*%Jonghyuk doubles over on the ground in uncontrollable laughter. This is the man you married.*Why are you looking at me like that? Are you planning on having your wicked way with me?$9_> I'm in love with whatever is wrong with you._Bahaha! Woof! Arf arf! Ruff. Growl.$11*%Jonghyuk doubles over on the ground in uncontrollable laughter. This is the man you married.*Why are you looking at me like that? Are you planning on having your wicked way with me?$9_> It's too early for this._Bahaha! Woof! Arf arf! Ruff. Growl.$11*%Jonghyuk doubles over on the ground in uncontrollable laughter. This is the man you married.*Why are you looking at me like that? Are you planning on having your wicked way with me?$9'",
  
  //GENDER NEUTRALITY COMPAT:
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.fall_25.GN": "Oh no. There's going to be a full moon tonight and I forgot to take my heat suppressant pills!$16#$b#Whatever will I do? All alone and vulnerable in front of my strong and reliable partner?$9#$b#$y '*How should you respond?_> Jonghyuk, what the heck?_Bahaha! Woof! Arf arf! Ruff. Growl.$11*%Jonghyuk doubles over on the ground in uncontrollable laughter. This is the man you married.*Why are you looking at me like that? Are you planning on having your wicked way with me?$9_> I'm in love with whatever is wrong with you._Bahaha! Woof! Arf arf! Ruff. Growl.$11*%Jonghyuk doubles over on the ground in uncontrollable laughter. This is the man you married.*Why are you looking at me like that? Are you planning on having your wicked way with me?$9_> It's too early for this._Bahaha! Woof! Arf arf! Ruff. Growl.$11*%Jonghyuk doubles over on the ground in uncontrollable laughter. This is the man you married.*Why are you looking at me like that? Are you planning on having your wicked way with me?$9'",

  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.winter_Jonghyuk": "Even when the world turns cold and pale white, you fill my life with warmth and color.$h#$b#Stay warm, my love. Though, I know plenty ways of keeping you warm if you ever need help remembering.$l",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.winter_7": "To be honest, I like fish only if it's been sliced and diced to oblivion.#$b#If you're participating tomorrow, just remember to have fun. I'll be there to cheer you on.$u#$b#Then I'll cook us a hearty dinner to warm us up. A celebratory feast for you and me.$9",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.winter_24": "I already have everything I could have wanted. With you, every day already feels like a celebration.$8#$b#You're the kind of gift that makes every ordinary moment feel extraordinary.$h",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.winter_28": "Thank you for making me feel so loved. I'm yours, @, this year, every year, always.$h#$b#I'm wishing you a happy New Year, my ${darling prince^beautiful queen}$. I'll be the man who keeps your crown straight and your world on fire.$l#$e#You are breathtaking, you are brilliant, and no one gets to hold you like I do, honey. I'm all yours.$9",

//Generic Dialogue

  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Day_0": "On the bright side, you won't have to water your crops today. Now you can spend more time with your handsome hubby.$h",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Day_1": "I'm scared of thunder. What ever should you do to comfort me in my time of distress?$l",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Day_2": "%Jonghyuk steps close and pulls you right into a bearhug. Your feet dangle helplessly in the air as he laughs and spins you around.#$b#Baby, you're like lightning in a bottle. I can't let you go now that I got ya~!$h#$b#But I know you wouldn't like that. I don't mind getting struck by your electric love every now and then though.$9#$b#%He gently sets you back down, but not before giving you a quick smooch.",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Day_3": "You're in luck, my love. The neighborhood ahjummas call me a triple threat husband.$h#$b#I can cook, I can clean, and I care for all your needs.$13#$b#I'm a three-in-one combo, satisfaction-guaranteed, loyal and affectionate with a no refund policy.$12#$e#Need some help out of those clothes? I got a warm towel fresh from the dryer.$u",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Day_4": "It's so sad, babe. %pet was hiding under our bed because they're terrified of thunder.#$b#They're okay now, but I think a cuddle session would make %pet feel a whole lot better. Care to join me on the couch?", 
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Day_5": "You've got this hold on me that no time or distance can break. Every time I see you, it's like I'm falling in love all over again too.$l#$b#Here's some coffee to start the day.$h [395]",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Day_6": "Mornin', Sunshine. I woke up a bit early to make us some breakfast. [210 211 350]$8#$b#Rain or shine, you're the light of my life, @.$u", 
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Day_7": "I'll still spend every second reminding you just how perfect you are. The world can call you beautiful, but only I know the fire beneath that softness, the storm in your smile.#$b# You're my home, my ruin, and the chaos I never want to recover from.$l",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Night_0": "If I could, I'd take every bit of pain from you and carry it myself.$14#$b#But since I can't, I'll keep pouring every ounce of love I have into you, so you never feel sad.#$b#You're not alone anymore, not for a second. I'm right here.$11",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Night_1": "You're in luck, my love. The neighborhood ahjummas call me a triple threat husband.$h#$b#I can cook, I can clean, and I care for all your needs.$13#$b#I'm a three-in-one combo, satisfaction-guaranteed, loyal and affectionate with a no refund policy.$12#$e#Need some help out of those clothes? I got a warm towel fresh from the dryer.$u",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Night_2": "I went out on a little run. The downpour reminds me of our secret waterfall hideaway.$15#$b#I hope the weather's been treating you kindly. How 'bout you help me peel my clothes off and we take a nice warm bath together? Mmm?$h",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Night_3": "%Jonghyuk steps close and pulls you right into a bearhug. Your feet dangle in the air as he sings and spins you around.#$b#Baby, you're like lightning in a bottle. I can't let you go now that I got ya~!$h#$b#But I know you wouldn't like that. I don't mind getting struck by your electric love every now and then though.$9#$b#%He gently sets you back down, but not before giving you a quick smooch.",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Night_4": "Are you planning on staying up later than the stars? You should go to bed, otherwise I can't fall asleep.$s#$b#%Jonghyuk wraps you into a warm hug, pulling you into his strong arms.#$b#How do you expect me to sleep when I can't hold you?$l", 

  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Night_5": "@? Honey?$19#$b#You're just standing there. Is something wrong?$14#$b#$y '*Jonghyuk looks worried. How should you respond?_> I'm lonely._I want you to know that no matter how hard life gets, I’ll never stop being the person who takes care of you.$8*You’re never walking through the storm by yourself, ${darling^wifey}$.$h*I’ll never tire of loving you, reassuring you, and showing you how much you matter.$l_> I'm having a bad day._My heart aches knowing how hard the day has been for you.$14*I’ll always be your safe place. Your reminder that you’re strong, capable, and loved.*You don’t have to be perfect, honey. You just have to be you, and that’s more than enough.$8_> I'm fine._Okay. Good.$10*Just know you don’t have to carry everything alone, I am here to shoulder the weight with you.$13*You’re stronger than you think, and I’ll keep reminding you of that every single day.$11'",

  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Night_6": "Am I really not getting a good night kiss?$19#$b#Just one? Pretty please?$h#$b#$y '*How should you respond?_> Alright, you don't have to beg._I thought you enjoyed my begging.$16*I'm never not polite for another kiss.$h*So how about another one?$9_> I'll give you more than one._You're making me blush.$l*It's so unfair. You really know how to make a man fall harder every time you speak.$9_> You're so needy._Only for you. What's with that cute little pout, my ${grumpy prince^darling princess}$?$13*You mad at me again and forgot to tell me why?$12*Either way... come here. Let me charm that frown off your pretty face, mm?$17'", //Be careful not to erase or overwrite the "_", "*" and the ">"

  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Night_7": "Am I really not getting a good night kiss?$19#$b#Just one? Pretty please?$h#$b#$y '*How should you respond?_> Alright, you don't have to beg._I thought you enjoyed my begging.$16*I'm never not polite for another kiss.$h*So how about another one?$9_> I'll give you more than one._You're making me blush.$l*It's so unfair. You really know how to make a man fall harder every time you speak.$9_> You're so needy._Only for you. What's with that cute little pout, my ${grumpy prince^darling princess}$?$13*You mad at me again and forgot to tell me why?$12*Either way... come here. Let me charm that frown off your pretty face, mm?$17'", //Be careful not to erase or overwrite the "_", "*" and the ">"
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Night_Jonghyuk": "Am I really not getting a good night kiss?$19#$b#Just one? Pretty please?$h#$b#$y '*How should you respond?_> Alright, you don't have to beg._I thought you enjoyed my begging.$16*I'm never not polite for another kiss.$h*So how about another one?$9_> I'll give you more than one._You're making me blush.$l*It's so unfair. You really know how to make a man fall harder every time you speak.$9_> You're so needy._Only for you. What's with that cute little pout, my ${grumpy prince^darling princess}$?$13*You mad at me again and forgot to tell me why?$12*Either way... come here. Let me charm that frown off your pretty face, mm?$17'", //Be careful not to erase or overwrite the "_", "*" and the ">"

  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Indoor_Day_0": "Hello, my dear ${hubby^wifey}$. Love of my life. The other half of my soul.$8#$b#$y '*How should you respond?$h_> Give him a kiss._If this isn't how I'm greeted every time, I'm gonna start the day all pouty and heartbroken, my beloved.$16*You've set the bar way too high now... Guess you'll just have to keep spoiling me like this forever, mmm?$9_> Give him a hug._If I could freeze time just to stay wrapped in your arms a little longer, I would. You make every sunrise worth waking up to.$9*Good morning, @. My wild heart.$h_> What's for breakfast?_Oh, you know! The usual. I'm starting to think that you fell in love with me just for my cooking![210 211 350]$u*Just make sure to kiss the chef on your way out, mmm?$l'", //Be careful not to erase or overwrite the "_", "*" and the ">"
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Indoor_Day_1": "Isn't it crazy?$h#$b#Every morning I wake up and look at you and then I think to myself...$8#$b#Damn, how is it possible that my ${hubby^wife}$ gets even more ${handsome^gorgeous}$ every single day?$h#$b#Anyways, here's some morning grub for my darling hub. Make sure to kiss the chef afterward, hm?$u[210 211 395]^Anyways, I made us some breakfast. A happy wife is a happy life. Make sure to kiss the chef afterward, hm?$u[210 211 395]",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Indoor_Day_2": "I just wanted to make the morning a little special for us, so I made a little something.#$b#But you know what? Nothing beats the comfort of just being with you at home. Next time, I’ll bring the coffee straight to you.  [210 211 618]",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Indoor_Day_3": "Good morning, my wild heart. I woke up smiling like a fool again. My dreams were full of you.$8#$b#If I could, I’d pull you back into bed and spend the whole morning wrapped around you. I'd be kissing that sleepy smile of yours awake.$h",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Indoor_Day_4": "You're in luck, my love. The neighborhood ahjummas call me a triple threat husband.$h#$b#I can cook, I can clean, and I care for all your needs.$13#$b#I'm a three-in-one combo, satisfaction-guaranteed, loyal and affectionate with a no refund policy.$12#$e#Here's a little something to snack on throughout the day.$u[223 228 651]", 
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Indoor_Day_5": "Aigoo... my @ senses are tingling. Something's off.#$b#What are you scheming this time, oh darling ${husband^wife}$ of mine?$11#$b#$y '*How should you respond?$h_> Would you still love me if I was a worm?_Bahah! Seriously? That's what was on your mind?$u*No star burns brighter than the love I feel for you! Even if you were a wriggly little worm.$h*%Jonghyuk plants a tender kiss on your forehead.*Mwah.$h^Mwah. A happy wife is a happy life.$15_> Boop him on the nose._Huh. This your plan, mm? Testing my patience while looking irresistibly cute?$u*You and I both know you want more than just to boop my nose, my love.$h*I'll make sure you never forget what happens if you keep teasing me like this.$15_> Kiss him on the cheek._You really know how to spoil me in the most beautiful ways, mmm?$u*Well, if you keep this up, I might just have to remind you how much I appreciate all that attention.$h*I'll make sure to return the favor in ways that'll leave you... panting.$15'", //Be careful not to erase or overwrite the "_", "*" and the ">"", 
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Indoor_Day_6": "I was doing the laundry and you'll never believe what happened.$12#$b#I found my favorite sock! And I know where the other one is!$11#$b#My little socks are finally going to be reunited and be so happy.$13#$e#I swear I'm not this scatterbrained. I just sometimes confuse my load with yours and they end up all washed together.$19",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Indoor_Day_7": "Hi, Honey. What's that word for when hands are bisexual?$19#$b#$y 'Jonghyuk looks painfully confused._> Do you mean ambidextrous?_I am so in love with you.$16_> What is wrong with you?_Hey, it was a genuine question!$19*Aigoo, it's on the tip of my tongue. I'm going to go insane once I find out what it is.$s'",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Indoor_Day_8": "Dr. Harvey is such a wonderful guy. He broke his own personal record on pull-ups the other day.$h#$b#He was genuinely so surprised. I love seeing people fall in love with themselves like that. Small and steady gains go a long way.$8",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Indoor_Night_0": "I won't be subtle about loving you. Not now. Not ever.$h#$b#I'll say it when you're in my arms, half-asleep, and still somehow the most ${handsome^beautiful}$ person I've ever seen.$l#$b#I'll love you loudly. Shamelessly. Completely.$9",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Indoor_Night_1": "You have no idea what you've done to me.$13#$b#You're the heartbeat of my melody, and I want all of it.$11#$b#Your laugh? Mine. Your kiss? Mine. Your everything? You already know.$16#$b#I don't intend to share. I don't even pretend to.$9",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Indoor_Night_2": "Are you planning on staying up later than the stars? C'mon, go to bed already.$l#$b#$y '*How should you respond?_> I'll be there in a minute._How do you expect me to sleep when I can't hold you?$h*Sweet dreams, my beloved.$15_> Hmm? I'm not feeling tired though~_Then don’t sleep. Stay tangled in me, and let the night consume us whole.$h*If rest dares to come, I’ll chase it away. Tonight, you are mine to keep awake, mine to worship, mine to burn with until dawn.$15'", //Be careful not to erase or overwrite the "_", "*" and the ">"
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Indoor_Night_3": "I never thought anyone could make my world feel this bright.#$b#But here you are, effortlessly lighting up everything even in the dead of night.$15#$b#You're my everything and I'm so thankful to have you by my side, @.$h",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Indoor_Night_4": "Am I really not getting a good night kiss? Just one, please?$s#$e#I'm never not polite for another kiss.$h#$e#How about another one?$l#$e#Keep staring, @. This face belongs to you. Every line, every look.$9#$b#But don't forget... when you admire your masterpiece too long, the artist always collects his due.$l#$e#I might just ask for a little more than a smooch... but I'm sure you wouldn't mind.$u",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Indoor_Night_5": "Welcome home, my wild heart. Here is your kiss.$l#$b#I made us some dinner. Can't let you sleep on an empty stomach!$l [206 212 215 224 237]",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Indoor_Night_6": "Am I really not getting a good night kiss?$19#$b#Just one? Pretty please?$h#$b#$y '*How should you respond?_> Alright, you don't have to beg._I thought you enjoyed my begging.$16*I'm never not polite for another kiss.$h*So how about another one?$9_> I'll give you more than one._You're making me blush.$l*It's so unfair. You really know how to make a man fall harder every time you speak.$9_> You're so needy._Only for you. What's with that cute little pout, my ${grumpy prince^darling princess}$?$13*You mad at me again and forgot to tell me why?$12*Either way... come here. Let me charm that frown off your pretty face, mm?$17'", //Be careful not to erase or overwrite the "_", "*" and the ">"
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Indoor_Night_7": "Are you planning on staying up later than the stars? You should go to bed, otherwise I can't fall asleep.$s#$b#%Jonghyuk wraps you into a warm hug, pulling you into his strong arms.#$b#How do you expect me to sleep when I can't hold you?$l",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Indoor_Night_8": "Am I really not getting a good night kiss? Just one, please?$s#$e#I'm never not polite for another kiss.$h#$e#How about another one?$l#$e#Keep staring, @. This face belongs to you. Every line, every look.$9#$b#But don't forget... when you admire your masterpiece too long, the artist always collects his due.$l#$e#I might just ask for a little more than a smooch... but I'm sure you wouldn't mind.$u",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Indoor_Night_9": "Yeah, this your plan, mm? Testing my patience while looking irresistibly cute?#$b#You have no idea how close I am to scooping you up, carrying you to bed, and making sure you never forget what happens when you keep me waiting this long.", 
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Indoor_Night_Jonghyuk": "Babe, %pet wanted me to go to bed and I said '5 more minutes' just once.$10#$b#That was 2 hours ago. %pet is still quietly waiting, watching me like they're negotiating with time itself.$11#$b#It's not the same without all of us in bed together. I wanted to wait for you.$12",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Outdoor_0": "Hey, Darling! You've got a scratch on your hand. Does it hurt?$19#$b#$y '*How should you respond?_> I'm fine._And here I thought you'd want an excuse to be babied by your very handsome husband.$h*But still, let me see it. You're not getting injured on my watch. If I could, I’d take every bit of pain from you and carry it myself.$10*But since I can’t, I’ll just have to keep pouring every ounce of love I have into you.$11_> Will you kiss it better?_Of course!$h*Why would you miss the chance to be babied by your very handsome husband.$u*Come here, let me see it. I'm gonna kiss it better and maybe spoil you a little... but only if you say please.$l_> Yeah, it kinda stings._It's a good thing I came prepared.$h*Come here, let me see it. I'm gonna kiss it better and maybe spoil you a little... but only if you say please.$l'",  //Be careful not to erase or overwrite the "_", "*" and the ">"
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Outdoor_1": "If the world saw you through my eyes, they'd finally understand what it means to be truly cherished.$8#$b#But honestly... the most beautiful part of it will be growing old with you.#$b#I should build us some rocking chairs so we can sit on the porch together. Gotta prepare for early retirement with my darling ${hubby^wifey}$.$h",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Outdoor_2": "I don't need the sun when I have your smile... and I don't need anything else as long as I get to hold your hand.$h#$b#Thank you for loving me the way you do, love.$16",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Outdoor_3": "It feels like I'm dreaming with my eyes wide open. I'm falling all over again, yet it's not something I need saving from.#$b#Some call it the honeymoon phase, but there's nothing temporary about the way I feel now, about you.#$e#Nothing feels more like forever when I'm by your side.$l",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Outdoor_4": "%Jonghyuk is wiping pearls of sweat from his brow with his shirt, the movement briefly exposing the defined ridges of his sculpted abs.#$b#Hello, my love. There's nothing like a good pump to really get the blood flowing.$u#$e#No matter how heavy your day is, I’ll always be here to remind you that you belong right here, with me.$8#$b#Loving you is the easiest, most natural thing I’ve ever done.$h",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Outdoor_5": "Huh? You wanna know how I stay so fit?$11#$b#Well, it's no secret that you're my greatest motivation.$16#$b#After all, this body belongs to you, babe.$9#$b#%He steps into your space and flexes his chest, playfully bouncing his pecs.#$e#It's a good day to work out. Hope you're still raring to go, especially with all the crops and animals.$h#$e#There's something about seeing you hard at work that really gets me going. Gosh, I'm so into you.$h#$b#If you've got too much to do with farm work, get me to run out for chores and errands. When I'm back home, I'll relieve all your tension.$8",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Outdoor_6": "Don't forget to check up on Spanner from time to time. Kid adores you. I mean, who can blame him? We are family, after all.$h", 
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Outdoor_7": "I'm out of energy. I need to recharge. Can you give me a hug?$s#$b#$y '*How should you respond?_> Am I your personal charger?_Exactly. Recharge me, hubby.$h^Exactly. Recharge me, wifey.$h_> Give him a hug_Yeah, that's exactly what I needed. You give me everything I need.$h_> No._Aww... But you know how needy I am for your affection.$11*Oh well. I'll try again later.$15'", //Be careful not to erase or overwrite the "_", "*" and the ">"
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Outdoor_8": "Good morning, my dear ${hubby^wifey}$. Love of my life. Half of my soul.$8#$b#$y '*How should you respond?_> Give him a smooch_If this isn’t how I’m greeted every morning, I’m gonna start the day all pouty and heartbroken, my beloved.$16*You’ve set the bar way too high now... Guess you’ll just have to keep spoiling me like this forever, mmm?$9_> Give him a hug_If I could freeze time just to stay wrapped in your arms a little longer, I would. You make every sunrise worth waking up to.$9*Good morning, @. My wild heart.$h'", //Be careful not to erase or overwrite the "_", "*" and the ">"
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Outdoor_9": "@.$14#$b#%Jonghyuk pulls you close to him, tracing light, absentminded patterns over your back.#$b#You're warm, love.$14#$b#$y '*How should you respond?$h_> That's because you're cold._Then warm me up.$16*%He chuckles, the vibrations rumbling against your body, before pressing a slow, lingering kiss to your forehead. Without a word, he burrows deeper into your arms. Just steady warmth and quiet, unconditional love._> I love you._I love you more.$h*And that's more than enough... you and I--just us... it's everything I'd ever need.$9*%He chuckles, the vibrations rumbling against your body, before pressing a slow, lingering kiss to your forehead. Without a word, he burrows deeper into your arms. Just steady warmth and quiet, unconditional love._> Are you feeling okay?_I'm just having a moment.$14*I've broken things. Ruined moments, burned bridges, and turned away when I should've held on.$14*But loving you? That was the only thing I ever got right from the start.$8*%He chuckles, the vibrations rumbling against your body, before pressing a slow, lingering kiss to your forehead. Without a word, he burrows deeper into your arms. Just steady warmth and quiet, unconditional love.'",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Outdoor_10": "%Jonghyuk is wiping pearls of sweat from his brow with his shirt, the movement briefly exposing the defined ridges of his sculpted abs.#$b#Hello, my wild heart. There's nothing like a good pump to really get the blood flowing.$u#$e#No matter how heavy your day is, I’ll always be here to remind you that you belong right here, with me.$8#$b#Loving you is the easiest, most natural thing I’ve ever done.$h",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Outdoor_Jonghyuk": "I'm out of energy. I need to recharge. Can you give me a hug?$s#$b#$y '*How should you respond?_> Am I your personal charger?_Exactly. Recharge me, hubby.$h^Exactly. Recharge me, wifey.$h_> Give him a hug._Yeah, that's exactly what I needed. You give me everything I need.$h_> No._Aww... But you know how needy I am for your affection.$11*Oh well. I'll try again later.$15'", 

  //Affection Dialogue

  "Jonghyuk.flirtuwu": "Hmm... my @ senses are tingling. Something's off.#$b#What are you scheming this time, @?$11#$b#$y '*How should you respond?$h_> Would you still love me if I was a worm?_Bahah! Seriously? That's what was on your mind?$u*No star burns brighter than the love I feel for you! Even if you were a wriggly little worm.$h*%Jonghyuk plants a tender kiss on your forehead.*Mwah.$h_> Boop him on the nose._Huh. This your plan, mm? Testing my patience while looking irresistibly cute?$u*You and I both know you want more than just to boop my nose, my love.$h*I'll make sure you never forget what happens if you keep teasing me like this.$15_> Kiss him on the cheek._You really know how to spoil me in the most beautiful ways, mmm?$u*Well, if you keep this up, I might just have to remind you how much I appreciate all that attention.$h'", //Be careful not to erase or overwrite the "_", "*" and the ">" THIS IS FOR 10H Dialogue if not married, but dating


  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Good_0": "Hello, dear ${hubby^wifey}$. Love of my life. The other half of my soul.$8#$b#$y '*How should you respond?$h_> Give him a smooch_If this isn't how I'm greeted every time, I'm gonna start the day all pouty and heartbroken, my beloved.$16*You've set the bar way too high now... Guess you'll just have to keep spoiling me like this forever, mmm?$9_> Give him a hug_If I could freeze time just to stay wrapped in your arms a little longer, I would. You make every sunrise worth waking up to.$9*I love you so damn much, with all that I am.$h_> Got any plans tonight?_Why? Are you asking me out on a date?$16*Now you've got me very curious, @. You can't just tease me like that and expect me to behave.$9*Go on, tell me what you've got going on.$16'",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Good_1": "My allergies are getting way better! I feel bad for avoiding %pet, but I make sure they know I love them so much, and that they're wanted and cared for.$8",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Good_2": "Aren't I the best husband? Correction. I'm the world champion, undefeated, hall-of-fame hubby who owns your lap.$u#$e#Every now and then, I might just ask for a little more than a smooch... but I'm sure you wouldn't mind, right?$h", 
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Good_3": "@? Honey?$19#$b#You're just standing there. Is something wrong?$14#$b#$y '*Jonghyuk looks worried. How should you respond?_> I'm lonely._I want you to know that no matter how hard life gets, I’ll never stop being the person who takes care of you.$8*You’re never walking through the storm by yourself, ${darling^wifey}$.$h*I’ll never tire of loving you, reassuring you, and showing you how much you matter.$l_> I'm having a bad day._My heart aches knowing how hard the day has been for you.$14*I’ll always be your safe place. Your reminder that you’re strong, capable, and loved.*You don’t have to be perfect, honey. You just have to be you, and that’s more than enough.$8_> I'm fine._Okay. Good.$10*Just know you don’t have to carry everything alone, I am here to shoulder the weight with you.$13*You’re stronger than you think, and I’ll keep reminding you of that every single day.$11'", //Be careful not to erase or overwrite the "_", "*" and the ">"
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Good_4": "Aigoo... my @ senses are tingling. Something's off.#$b#What are you scheming this time, oh darling ${husband^wife}$ of mine?$11#$b#$y '*How should you respond?$h_> Would you still love me if I was a worm?_Bahah! Seriously? That's what was on your mind?$u*No star burns brighter than the love I feel for you! Even if you were a wriggly little worm.$h*%Jonghyuk plants a tender kiss on your forehead.*Mwah.$h^Mwah. A happy wife is a happy life.$15_> Boop him on the nose._Huh. This your plan, mm? Testing my patience while looking irresistibly cute?$u*You and I both know you want more than just to boop my nose, my love.$h*I'll make sure you never forget what happens if you keep teasing me like this.$15_> Kiss him on the cheek._You really know how to spoil me in the most beautiful ways, mmm?$u*Well, if you keep this up, I might just have to remind you how much I appreciate all that attention.$h*I'll make sure to return the favor in ways that'll leave you... panting.$15'",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Good_5": "Ezra and Iman ambushed me the other day. I was just minding my own business when they suddenly swooped me into their store.$19#$b#Next thing I know, I was trying on clothes left and right. It was kind of fun, actually.$h#$b#Ezra's convinced that I'd make a good model for their clothing brand. Do you think I should take him up on his offer?#$b#$y '*How should you respond?$h_> Can I watch?_Babe, I'd make sure you'd have a front row seat!$h*Honestly, I think I'd get nervous in front of a crowd. But if you're in the audience...$15*I know I could pull this off.$h_> Of course. I know you'll do well._...!$l*It's wild. You have no idea just how lovable you are. Like genuinely.$9*Having your whole trust in me beyond a shadow of a doubt makes my heart feel so incredibly full.*Honestly, I think I'd get nervous in front of a crowd. But if you're in the audience...$15*I know I could pull this off.$h_> No. I want you all to myself._...!$l*Oh my. Getting all possessive over me? Straight out of my dreams. I'm obsessed, and I hope you know it, @.$9'",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Good_6": "It's fun to help Maia every now and then to watch over Amina.$8#$b#Last time, I was invited to a tea party that somehow ended up turning into a murder mystery. Mr. Bear was an unlikely accomplice.$19#$b#...I think she's been watching too many soap operas on Miyoung's TV.$h",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Good_7": "@.$14#$b#%Jonghyuk pulls you close to him, tracing light, absentminded patterns over your back.#$b#You're warm, love.$14#$b#$y '*How should you respond?$h_> That's because you're cold._Then warm me up.$16*%He chuckles, the vibrations rumbling against your body, before pressing a slow, lingering kiss to your forehead. Without a word, he burrows deeper into your arms. Just steady warmth and quiet, unconditional love._> I love you._I love you more.$h*And that's more than enough... you and I--just us... it's everything I'd ever need.$9*%He chuckles, the vibrations rumbling against your body, before pressing a slow, lingering kiss to your forehead. Without a word, he burrows deeper into your arms. Just steady warmth and quiet, unconditional love._> Are you feeling okay?_I'm just having a moment.$14*I've broken things. Ruined moments, burned bridges, and turned away when I should've held on.$14*But loving you? That was the only thing I ever got right from the start.$8*%He chuckles, the vibrations rumbling against your body, before pressing a slow, lingering kiss to your forehead. Without a word, he burrows deeper into your arms. Just steady warmth and quiet, unconditional love.'",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Good_8": "I've never been good at soft things before. But you? You make me want to be gentle.$u#$b#$y '*How should you respond?$h_> You're so cute._Cute? Being this loveable is a full-time job. You know I'm powerless against you.$19_> You don't have to be gentle with me._Mm, dangerous words, ${hubby^wifey}$... How do you say things like that and expect me NOT to sweep you off your feet and make you forget how to even breathe?$h_> You're so annoying._What's with that cute little pout, my grumpy ${prince^wife}$?$13*You mad at me again and forgot to tell me why? Or are you just looking for an excuse to have me kiss it better?$12*Either way... come here. Let me charm that frown off your pretty face, mm?$17'",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Good_9": "You already give me the happiest life just by being with me. I feel so complete with you, and all I want is to keep cherishing you the way you deserve.$8#$b#I can’t imagine life without you now.$h",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Good_10": "It's fun to help Maia every now and then to watch over Amina!$8#$b#Last time, I was invited to a tea party that somehow ended up turning into a murder mystery. Mr. Bear was an unlikely accomplice.$19#$b#...I think she's been watching too many soap operas on Miyoung's TV.$h",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Good_11": "Spanner fixed up our sink the other day! Wren's doing a wonderful job showing him the ropes.$8#$b#$y '*Now's a good time to ask any questions._> Why does he call you 'Boss?'_It just kinda stuck. I took him under my wing and we did a lot of odd jobs together back in Zuzu.*He used to have a really bad temper and get in all sorts of trouble, but I take good care of my people.$h_> How did you two first meet?_I caught him stealing from a fruit vendor once.$10*He was following the wrong sorts of people back then. Let's just say that I was in the right place at the right time.$11_> What's up with him and fire?_You have no idea. It's weird and paranormal.$19*Spanner loves studing dwarven technology and applying what he knows to his own devices.$8*Something usually ends up combusting into flames because of it. At least we have a resident firefighter nearby.$h'",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Good_12": "Am I really not getting a goodbye kiss?$19#$b#Just one? Pretty please?$h#$b#$y '*How should you respond?_> Alright, you don't have to beg._I thought you enjoyed my begging.$16*I'm never not polite for another kiss.$h*So how about another one?$9_> I'll give you more than one._You're making me blush.$l*It's so unfair. You really know how to make a man fall harder every time you speak.$9_> You're so needy._Only for you. What's with that cute little pout, my ${grumpy prince^darling princess}$?$13*You mad at me again and forgot to tell me why?$12*Either way... come here. Let me charm that frown off your pretty face, mm?$17'",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Good_13": "Damn, I'm luckiest man in the world to wake up to this view.$h#$b#Oh, the farm is pretty too.$l",

  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Neutral_0": "%Jonghyuk seems pretty quiet this morning.#$b#What? Sorry, I was just thinking about stuff.#$b#It's silly, but sometimes I wonder if it's okay to be happy like this.#$b#I broke things. I've ruined moments, burned bridges, and turned away when I should've held on. But loving you? That was one of the only things I ever got right from the start.",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Neutral_1": "%Jonghyuk is wiping pearls of sweat from his brow with his shirt, the movement briefly exposing the defined ridges of his sculpted abs.#$b#Hello, my wild heart. There's nothing like a good pump to really get the blood flowing.$u#$e#No matter how heavy your day is, I’ll always be here to remind you that you belong right here, with me.$8#$b#Loving you is the easiest, most natural thing I’ve ever done.$h",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Neutral_2": "I will still like you, even when we're old and shriveled up.$u#$b#Haha, don't take offense! You know what they say, wine improves with age...$h",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Neutral_3": "@? Honey?$19#$b#You're just standing there. Is something wrong?$14#$b#$y '*Jonghyuk looks worried. How should you respond?_> I'm lonely._I want you to know that no matter how hard life gets, I’ll never stop being the person who takes care of you.$8*You’re never walking through the storm by yourself, ${darling^wifey}$.$h*I’ll never tire of loving you, reassuring you, and showing you how much you matter.$l_> I'm having a bad day._My heart aches knowing how hard the day has been for you.$14*I’ll always be your safe place. Your reminder that you’re strong, capable, and loved.*You don’t have to be perfect, honey. You just have to be you, and that’s more than enough.$8_> I'm fine._Okay. Good.$10*Just know you don’t have to carry everything alone, I am here to shoulder the weight with you.$13*You’re stronger than you think, and I’ll keep reminding you of that every single day.$11'",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Neutral_4": "Spanner fixed up our sink the other day! Wren's doing a wonderful job showing him the ropes.$8#$b#$y '*Now's a good time to ask any questions._> Why does he call you 'Boss?'_It just kinda stuck. I took him under my wing and we did a lot of odd jobs together back in Zuzu.*He used to have a really bad temper and get in all sorts of trouble, but I take good care of my people.$h_> How did you two first meet?_I caught him stealing from a fruit vendor once.$10*He was following the wrong sorts of people back then. Let's just say that I was in the right place at the right time.$11_> What's up with him and fire?_You have no idea. It's weird and paranormal.$19*Spanner loves studing dwarven technology and applying what he knows to his own devices.$8*Something usually ends up combusting into flames because of it. At least we have a resident firefighter nearby.$h'", //Duplicate of an earlier code.
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Neutral_5": "Life can be unbearably heavy at times, but please know you’ll never have to face it without me.$2#$b#If my words give you comfort, then I’ll keep speaking them until you never doubt your strength again. I’ll always be the hand pulling you back up if you ever stumble.$h",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Neutral_6": "Wren has been lending me some of her books. Maybe we could cuddle on the couch and read them together.$l", 
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Neutral_8": "Dr. Harvey has been working really hard lately. He broke his own personal record on pull-ups!$h#$b#He was so surprised. I love seeing people fall in love with themselves like that. Small and steady gains go a long way.$8", 
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Bad_0": "You're upset with me, aren't you? I can't remedy this situation if you don't tell me why.", 
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Bad_1": "Look, I'm not perfect. If I've done something wrong, just tell me. I'll try and be a better man.", 
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Bad_2": "If anything's bothering you, you know you can tell me...$s",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Bad_3": "Hey. All I want is for you to feel safe and cherished with me.$s#$b#Love like ours doesn’t come often, and I don’t take it for granted. You are everything to me.#$b#I'm right here... Please don't shut me out.$s", 
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Bad_4": "@? Honey?$19#$b#You're just standing there. Is something wrong?$14#$b#$y '*Jonghyuk looks worried. How should you respond?_> I'm lonely._I want you to know that no matter how hard life gets, I’ll never stop being the person who takes care of you.$8*You’re never walking through the storm by yourself, ${darling^wifey}$.$h*I’ll never tire of loving you, reassuring you, and showing you how much you matter.$l_> I'm having a bad day._My heart aches knowing how hard the day has been for you.$14*I’ll always be your safe place. Your reminder that you’re strong, capable, and loved.*You don’t have to be perfect, honey. You just have to be you, and that’s more than enough.$8_> I'm fine._Okay. Good.$10*Just know you don’t have to carry everything alone, I am here to shoulder the weight with you.$13*You’re stronger than you think, and I’ll keep reminding you of that every single day.$11'",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Bad_5": "If I could, I'd take every bit of pain from you and carry it myself.$14#$b#But since I can't, I'll keep pouring every ounce of love I have into you, so you never feel sad.#$b#You're not alone anymore, not for a second. I'm right here.$11",

  //GNMT COMPAT

  //Duplicates
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spouseRoom_Jonghyuk.1.GN": "I wanted to make the morning a little special for us so I whipped up a little something.$8#$b#But you know what? Nothing beats the comfort of just being with you at home.[210 211 395]$h#$b#Just make sure to kiss the chef on your way out, mmm?$l",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spouseRoom_Jonghyuk.2.GN": "Hi, Love. The farm life isn't quite what I imaged.$13#$b#You've turned moments into memories I'll treasure forever.$11#$b#Just knowing I bring you happiness and boundless love... there's no greater gift I could ask for.$9",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spouseRoom_Jonghyuk.3.GN": "We could watch the 'Queen of Sauce' together. But knowing you, I'd likely end up getting lost in the sauce.#$b#You can be kind of distracting. It's a good problem to have, I assure you. After all, you have my fully undivided attention.$l",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spouseRoom_Jonghyuk.4.GN": "Aigoo... my @ senses are tingling. Something's off.#$b#What are you scheming this time, oh darling partner of mine?$11#$b#$y '*How should you respond?$h_> Would you still love me if I was a worm?_Bahah! Seriously? That's what was on your mind?$u*No star burns brighter than the love I feel for you! Even if you were a wriggly little worm.$h*%Jonghyuk plants a tender kiss on your forehead.*Mwah.$h_> Boop him on the nose._Huh. This your plan, mm? Testing my patience while looking irresistibly cute?$u*You and I both know you want more than just to boop my nose, my love.$h*I'll make sure you never forget what happens if you keep teasing me like this.$15_> Kiss him on the cheek._You really know how to spoil me in the most beautiful ways, mmm?$u*Well, if you keep this up, I might just have to remind you how much I appreciate all that attention.$h*I'll make sure to return the favor in ways that'll leave you... panting.$15'", //Be careful not to erase or overwrite the "_", "*" and the ">"
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spouseRoom_Jonghyuk.5.GN": "I was doing the laundry and you'll never believe what happened.$12#$b#I found my favorite sock! And I know where the other one is!$11#$b#My socks are finally going to be reunited and be so happy.$13#$b#...I swear I'm not this scatterbrained. I just sometimes confuse my load with yours and they end up all washed together.$19#$e#What, did you need something? Wanted to see see me in my special socks?$11#$b#$y '*How should you respond?$h_> 'Just' your socks?_Ayo? How forward of you. Damn, you're making me blush.$h*I mean, if that's something you're into, then hell yeah. I'll give you a real show tonight and put them on nice and slow.$15*_> You forgot your kiss._You really know how to spoil me in the most beautiful ways.$h*Well, c'mere. I won't be subtle about loving you. Not now. Not ever.$l'",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spouseRoom_Jonghyuk.6.GN": "I don't mind if you read from my journal. I've had it for years now.#$b#I find journaling as a form of mediation. Helps me unravel my own feelings and figure out what I want to do at the moment.$h#$e#It's nice knowing you're interested in my drabbles. I enjoy sharing bits of my past with you like this.$8",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spouseRoom_Jonghyuk.7.GN": "My allergies to %pet are getting a whole lot better! Marnie suggested some hypoallergenic diets for our critters and they work like a charm.$8#$b#Now I can give $pet all the belly rubs and pets.$h#$e#What? You think %pet is cute? Well, I'm obviously cuter.$u",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spouseRoom_Jonghyuk.8.GN": "I've never been good at soft things. But you? You make me want to be gentle.$h#$b#How about we cuddle on the couch? I'll hold you with care, kiss with reverence, and speak to you with utmost tenderness.$16#$b#Aha, sorry if I'm getting a little sappy. I'll love you even more shamelessly.$9",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spouseRoom_Jonghyuk.9.GN": "Aigoo... my @ senses are tingling. Something's off.#$b#What are you scheming this time, oh darling partner of mine?$11#$b#$y '*How should you respond?$h_> Would you still love me if I was a worm?_Bahah! Seriously? That's what was on your mind?$u*No star burns brighter than the love I feel for you! Even if you were a wriggly little worm.$h*%Jonghyuk plants a tender kiss on your forehead.*Mwah.$h_> Boop him on the nose._Huh. This your plan, mm? Testing my patience while looking irresistibly cute?$u*You and I both know you want more than just to boop my nose, my love.$h*I'll make sure you never forget what happens if you keep teasing me like this.$15_> Kiss him on the cheek._You really know how to spoil me in the most beautiful ways, mmm?$u*Well, if you keep this up, I might just have to remind you how much I appreciate all that attention.$h*I'll make sure to return the favor in ways that'll leave you... panting.$15'", //Be careful not to erase or overwrite the "_", "*" and the ">"
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.spouseRoom_Jonghyuk.10.GN": "Hello, my dear @. Love of my life. The other half of my soul.$8#$b#$y '*How should you respond?$h_> Give him a kiss._If this isn't how I'm greeted every time, I'm gonna start the day all pouty and heartbroken, my beloved.$16*You've set the bar way too high now... Guess you'll just have to keep spoiling me like this forever, mmm?$9_> Give him a hug._If I could freeze time just to stay wrapped in your arms a little longer, I would. You make every sunrise worth waking up to.$9*Good morning, @. My wild heart.$h_> What's for breakfast?_Oh, you know! The usual. I'm starting to think that you fell in love with me just for my cooking![210 211 350]$u*Just make sure to kiss the chef on your way out, mmm?$l'", //Be careful not to erase or overwrite the "_", "*" and the ">" GENDER NEUTRAL COMPAT,

  //GMNT COMPAT - RAINY NIGHT

  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Day_0.GN": "On the bright side, you won't have to water your crops today. Now you can spend more time with your handsome hubby.$h",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Day_1.GN": "I'm scared of thunder. What ever should you do to comfort me in my time of distress?$l",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Day_2.GN": "%Jonghyuk steps close and pulls you right into a bearhug. Your feet dangle helplessly in the air as he laughs and spins you around.#$b#Baby, you're like lightning in a bottle. I can't let you go now that I got ya~!$h#$b#But I know you wouldn't like that. I don't mind getting struck by your electric love every now and then though.$9#$b#%He gently sets you back down, but not before giving you a quick smooch.",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Day_3.GN": "You're in luck, my love. The neighborhood ahjummas call me a triple threat husband.$h#$b#I can cook, I can clean, and I care for all your needs.$13#$b#I'm a three-in-one combo, satisfaction-guaranteed, loyal and affectionate with a no refund policy.$12#$e#Need some help out of those clothes? I got a warm towel fresh from the dryer.$u",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Day_4.GN": "It's so sad, babe. %pet was hiding under our bed because they're terrified of thunder.#$b#They're okay now, but I think a cuddle session would make %pet feel a whole lot better. Care to join me on the couch?", 
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Day_5.GN": "You've got this hold on me that no time or distance can break. Every time I see you, it's like I'm falling in love all over again too.$l#$b#Here's some coffee to start the day.$h [395]",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Day_6.GN": "Mornin', Sunshine. I woke up a bit early to make us some breakfast. [210 211 350]$8#$b#Rain or shine, you're the light of my life, @.$u", 
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Day_7.GN": "I'll still spend every second reminding you just how perfect you are. The world can call you beautiful, but only I know the fire beneath that softness, the storm in your smile.#$b# You're my home, my ruin, and the chaos I never want to recover from.$l",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Night_0.GN": "If I could, I'd take every bit of pain from you and carry it myself.$14#$b#But since I can't, I'll keep pouring every ounce of love I have into you, so you never feel sad.#$b#You're not alone anymore, not for a second. I'm right here.$11",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Night_1.GN": "You're in luck, my love. The neighborhood ahjummas call me a triple threat husband.$h#$b#I can cook, I can clean, and I care for all your needs.$13#$b#I'm a three-in-one combo, satisfaction-guaranteed, loyal and affectionate with a no refund policy.$12#$e#Need some help out of those clothes? I got a warm towel fresh from the dryer.$u",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Night_2.GN": "I went out on a little run. The downpour reminds me of our secret waterfall hideaway.$15#$b#I hope the weather's been treating you kindly. How 'bout you help me peel my clothes off and we take a nice warm bath together? Mmm?$h",
  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Night_3.GN": "%Jonghyuk steps close and pulls you right into a bearhug. Your feet dangle in the air as he sings and spins you around.#$b#Baby, you're like lightning in a bottle. I can't let you go now that I got ya~!$h#$b#But I know you wouldn't like that. I don't mind getting struck by your electric love every now and then though.$9#$b#%He gently sets you back down, but not before giving you a quick smooch.",

  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Night_4.GN": "Are you planning on staying up later than the stars? You should go to bed, otherwise I can't fall asleep.$s#$b#%Jonghyuk wraps you into a warm hug, pulling you into his strong arms.#$b#How do you expect me to sleep when I can't hold you?$l", 

  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Night_5.GN": "@? Honey?$19#$b#You're just standing there. Is something wrong?$14#$b#$y '*Jonghyuk looks worried. How should you respond?_> I'm lonely._I want you to know that no matter how hard life gets, I’ll never stop being the person who takes care of you.$8*You’re never walking through the storm by yourself, darling.$h*I’ll never tire of loving you, reassuring you, and showing you how much you matter.$l_> I'm having a bad day._My heart aches knowing how hard the day has been for you.$14*I’ll always be your safe place. Your reminder that you’re strong, capable, and loved.*You don’t have to be perfect, honey. You just have to be you, and that’s more than enough.$8_> I'm fine._Okay. Good.$10*Just know you don’t have to carry everything alone, I am here to shoulder the weight with you.$13*You’re stronger than you think, and I’ll keep reminding you of that every single day.$11'",


  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Night_6.GN": "Am I really not getting a good night kiss?$19#$b#Just one? Pretty please?$h#$b#$y '*How should you respond?_> Alright, you don't have to beg._I thought you enjoyed my begging.$16*I'm never not polite for another kiss.$h*So how about another one?$9_> I'll give you more than one._You're making me blush.$l*It's so unfair. You really know how to make a man fall harder every time you speak.$9_> You're so needy._Only for you. What's with that cute little pout, my love?$13*You mad at me again and forgot to tell me why?$12*Either way... come here. Let me charm that frown off your pretty face, mm?$17'", //Be careful not to erase or overwrite the "_", "*" and the ">"


  "Jonghyuk.Marriage.Rainy_Night_7.GN": "Am I really not getting a good night kiss?$19#$b#Just one? Pretty please?$h#$b#$y '*How should you respond?_> Alright, you don't have to beg._I thought you enjoyed my begging.$16*I'm never not polite for another kiss.$h*So how about another one?$9_> I'll give you more than one._You're making me blush.$l*It's so unfair. You really know how to make a man fall harder every time you speak.$9_> You're so needy._Only for you. What's with that cute little pout, my love$?$13*You mad at me again and forgot to tell me why?$12*Either way... come here. Let me charm that frown off your pretty face, mm?$17'", //Be careful not to erase or overwrite the "_", "*" and the ">"
